videos.headline: Melrose says NHL going through same thing as NFL on hits
videos.description: Barry Melrose says that Taylor Hall's hit on Philip Larsen looked clean, but it was a split-second decision for the referees to not call a penalty, and it will still be discussed throughout the hockey world.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NHL Analysis (Melrose says NHL going through same thing as NFL on hits) 2016/12/06 SVP SC
